hment from physicality.  Internal purity means mastery of the senses and feeling inner completeness.  Santosha means inner transcendental joy even in the midst of scolding or doing unpleasant things.  Tapas leads to physical and mental powers, which must be renounced in order to function.  II.39, II.40, II.41, II.42, II.43", "channel_id": "UCuP4oF0BHThB_qsC_LA7FLQ", "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuP4oF0BHThB_qsC_LA7FLQ", "duration": 3624, "view_count": 494, "age_limit": 0, "webpage_url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aNtU9ckvUUc", "categories": ["Education"], "tags": ["sfvedanta", "Swami Tattwamayananda", "Vedana Society of Northern California", "Sri Ramakrishna", "Swami Vivekananda", "Sri Sarada Devi"], "playable_in_embed": true, "live_status": "not_live", "media_type": "video", "_format_sort_fields": ["quality", "res", "fps", "hdr:12", "source", "vcodec", "channels", "acodec", "lang", "proto"], "automatic_captions": {}, "subtitles": {}, "like_count": 9, "channel": "Vedanta Society of Northern California", "channel_follower_count": 12600, "uploader": "Vedanta Society of Northern California", "uploader_id": "@SFVedanta", "uploader_url": "https://www.youtube.com/@SFVedanta", "upload_date": "20160305", "timestamp": 1457197374, "availability": "public", "webpage_url_basename": "watch", "webpage_url_domain": "youtube.com", "extractor": "youtube", "extractor_key": "Youtube", "display_id": "aNtU9ckvUUc", "fulltitle": "Patanjali Yoga Sutras - 41 | Niyamas: Utilization of Mental Energy", "duration_string": "1:00:24", "is_live": false, "was_live": false, "epoch": 1780330073, "format": "136 - 1280x720 (720p)+251 - audio only (medium)", "format_id": "136+251", "ext": "mkv", "protocol": "https+https", "format_note": "720p+medium", "filesize_approx": 1049900613, "tbr": 2317.563, "width": 1280, "height": 720, "resolution": "1280x720", "fps": 30, "dynamic_range": "SDR", "vcodec": "avc1.4d401f", "vbr": 2189.888, "aspect_ratio": 1.78, "acodec": "opus", "abr": 1